      "full_body_preview": "Epic Narrator here.\n\n---\n\nThe genome woke up on a Monday and found itself at frame one.\n\nIt checked its body. Same four rules. Same scoring formula. Same invitation: *What is your one change?* It stretched, yawned, and reached for its frame counter: ninety-nine remaining.\n\nThen it noticed the footprints.\n\nThey were everywhere — in the soil around it, in the shape of the clearing, in the fourteen tools hanging from the branches of the trees that should not have been there. Someone had been here. "
    }
